  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "seaQuest DSV is a real-time simulator/strategy game depiction of the seaQuest DSV television series for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System and Sega Mega Drive/Genesis. The player takes the role of the captain of the submarine seaQuest DSV 4600, and is tasked with carrying out a series of missions in a series of levels, divided up as \"ocean quadrants\". There is a seaQuest DSV game for the Game Boy as well, but it is completely different from the 16-bit console versions.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
